================================================================================
PART III — INNOVATION RECOGNITION & SPECIFIC CLAIMS
================================================================================

The following scientific innovations are the exclusive intellectual contribution
of Xavier Callens and MUST be attributed in any derived publication or product:

  1. FLAGNO (Field-Aligned Graph Network Optimization) — O(1) weak-scaling
     anisotropic preconditioning for XMHD plasma simulations.

  2. Neuro-Symbolic SUNDIALS Bridge — Memory-safe Rust integration of LLNL
     SUNDIALS with formally verified ML topologies via Lean 4.

  3. Quantized Tensor Train (QTT) XMHD Integration — Phase-space folding for
     6D gyrokinetic Boltzmann equations on commodity hardware.

  4. Asynchronous LSS Adjoint Decoupling — CPU/GPU chaos-decoupled control
     for real-time fusion plasma via Least Squares Shadowing.

  5. PSC Protocol Stack (K–O) — Quantum-photonic, acoustofluidic, and
     adjoint-guided RuBisCO enzyme evolution for 72,000 t CO₂/km²/yr yield.

  6. SOP Reproducibility Platform — Community-executable scientific SOP
     framework integrated into GCP serverless Mission Control.

  7. Kalundborg 2.0 EIP Topology Optimizer — Global eco-industrial park
     placement via geo-optimization for planetary regeneration.

